      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single blemish, and the interior still carries that new-car scent with perfectly preserved upholstery. Every mechanical and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, making this a true collector-grade find for the most demanding enthusiast.",
