    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car performs well on the road, the exterior shows clear signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some sun-fading on the roof. The interior is clean but shows typical wear and tear on the seats and carpets from regular use. All major features, including the air conditioning and audio system, are fully functional, making this a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer.",
