    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that is truly indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like clarity with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches, further enhanced by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather still carries its original factory aroma, the bolsters show no signs of compression, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every button, dial, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. It comes complete with all original manuals, both master keys, and a clean title. We welcome and encourage any third-party professional inspection to confirm that this is one of the finest examples currently available on the market.",
